#. Tag: para
#: startupview.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Startup View is shown at startup and when <menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem></menuchoice> is selected."
msgstr ""
"Zagonski pogled je prikazan ob zagonu in ko je izbrana "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Nova</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: startupview.docbook:4
#, no-c-format
msgid "It has 3 sections for:"
msgstr "Ima 3 razdelke za:"

#. Tag: para
#: startupview.docbook:7
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Creation of new projects. See also <link linkend=\"creating-a-project"
"\">Creating a Project</link> and <link linkend=\"managing-resources"
"\">Managing Resources</link>&nbsp;"
msgstr ""
"Ustvarjanje novih projektov. Glejte tudi <link linkend=\"creating-a-project"
"\">Ustvarjanje projekta</link> in <link linkend=\"managing-resources"
"\">Upravljanje virov</link>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: startupview.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opening existing projects. This section gives you the possibility to open an "
"existing project file or one of the 10 most recent projects you have opened."
msgstr ""
"Odpiranje obstoječih projektov. Ta razdelek vam daje možnost, da odprete "
"obstoječo projektno datoteko ali enega od 10 zadnjih projektov, ki ste jih "
"odprli."

#. Tag: para
#: startupview.docbook:9
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Help section gives you links to introductory pages, documentation and "
"community forum."
msgstr ""
"V razdelku Pomoč so povezave do uvodnih strani, dokumentacije in foruma "
"skupnosti."
